\dfrac{∂f}{∂θ_i}=trace(\dfrac{∂A}{∂θ_i}A^T+A\dfrac{∂A}{∂θ_i}^T)=2trace(A\dfrac{∂A}{∂θ_i})\in\mathbb{R}
