f(\theta)=trace(A^2)=trace(\sum_{i,j}G_{i,j}G_{i,j}^T\sum_{k,l}G_{k,l}G_{k,l}^T)=\sum_{i,j,k,l}trace(G_{i,j}G_{i,j}^TG_{k,l}G_{k,l}^T)=\sum_{i,j,k,l}trace(G_{k,l}^TG_{i,j}G_{i,j}^TG_{k,l})=\sum_{i,j,k,l}(G_{k,l}^TG_{i,j})^2
