\frac{\partial}{\partial a_{uv}}\|A\| = \frac{1}{\|A\|}a_{uv}
\frac{\partial}{\partial a_{uv}}\|A\|^{-2}=-2\,\|A\|^{-3}\frac{1}{\|A\|} a_{uv}=\frac{-2}{\|A\|^4}a_{uv}
A=\sum_i \sum_j G_{i,j}G_{i,j}^T \hspace{2em} a_{uv}=\sum_i\sum_j G_{ij;u}G_{ij;v}
\frac{\partial a_{uv}}{\partial \theta}= \sum_i\sum_j \left( \frac{\partial G_{ij;u}}{\partial{\theta}}G_{ij;v} +  G_{ij;u}\frac{\partial G_{ij;v}}{\partial{\theta}} \right)
\frac{\partial}{\partial \theta}\|A\|^{-2} = \frac{-2}{\|A\|^4} \sum_{u} \sum_{v} \frac{\partial a_{uv}}{\partial \theta}
